    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "## Beacon Chain [PR #2554]\r\n- [x] Use ALTAIR_FORK_EPOCH instead of ALTAIR_FORK_SLOT (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2342)\r\n- [x] Provide function for starting cleanly from Altair specification (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2323) => it's done in #2529\r\n- [x] Altair comments and minor logic cleanups (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2374) => reorder conditions in `process_attestations`, we did that already\r\n- [ ] Remove sync committee aggregates list in favor if a single aggregate (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2370)\r\n- [ ] Adjust sync committee size and duration (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2371)\r\n- [ ] [Bugfix] Use stable sync committee indices when processing block rewards (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2394)\r\n- [x] Clarify fork upgrade conditions for Altair (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2404) => just some comments added, nothing to do\r\n- [ ] Restrict sync committee period calculation boundaries (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2406)\r\n- [ ] Participation flag and incentive review (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2399)\r\n- [ ] Update inactivity penalty deltas processing (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2395)\r\n- [ ] Ensure indices are ordered [source, target, head] everywhere (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2411)\r\n- [ ] Map attestation participation to flag deltas in fork transition (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2373, https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2408)\r\n- [ ] Enhanced Altair testing (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2334, https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2363)\r\n\r\n## Validator  [PR #2554]\r\n- [ ] Adjust subnet count to reflect smaller sync committees (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2376)\r\n- [ ] Add logic for handling sync committee assignment off by one issue (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2400)\r\n- [ ] Update validator guide with restricted sync committee computation (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2407)\r\n- [ ] Return non-duplicated sync committee subnets (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2409)\r\n\r\n## Network  [PR #2554]\r\n- [x] Respect subcommittees in gossip validations for Altair (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2329)\r\n- [x] Add syncnets data to Altair MetaData (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2352)\r\n- [ ] Minor naming cleanup (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2362)\r\n- [x] Add logic for handling sync committee assignment off by one issue (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2400)\r\n- [ ] BlocksByRange under weak subjectivity (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2131) => opened #2556\r\n- [ ] Remove ResourceUnavailable error code for more discussion (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2413)\r\n\r\n## Sync Protocol  [PR #2554]\r\n- [ ] Updates to Altair light client sync protocol (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2378)\r\n",
